                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.51/1514.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-31T15:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 31, 1915—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your March 12, 9 a.m., Department’s March 18, 5 p.m., reference credit order
                    1334. In Department’s opinion authorization by Dominican Congress necessary.
                    Department therefore disapproved credit order 1334.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
